[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1056[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1057[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: the handoff arrives at the coordinator without the prescreen artifacts, without the patient-reported flags, without the patient's stated questions, or without the patient-confirmed follow-up arrangement. Each of those creates coordinator rework, patient frustration, or both. The patient who was promised a same-day callback and waited three days because the SLA was over-promised is the patient who disengages from the trial. The handoff is the operational deliverable; the conversation is the means.
