[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1061[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 6: Run continuous safety screening across every patient utterance.** Same as the prior chapter 11 recipes: every utterance runs through the continuous safety tap, and acute emergencies preempt the recruitment conversation with emergency-pathway routing.
