[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1112[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1113[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: an acute emergency disclosure by a patient in a recruitment conversation goes unhandled. The recruitment conversation is not the place to triage acute emergencies; the architecture's job is to recognize them and route them out. Skipping or weakening continuous safety screening is the most consequential single mistake the architecture can make.
