[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1116[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1117[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 7: Persist the IRB-grade audit record and emit lifecycle events for analytics.** Every conversation produces records. The records are tamper-evident, version-stamped, and retained per the institutional research-data-retention policy and per trial-specific retention requirements.
